  "2026-06-25T17:41:04.644Z",codex-gpt5,"Investigation note: the concrete worker reconnect/healthcheck fix surface is scripts/prod/telemetry, which is intentionally git-ignored as private production operations material. I validated the needed local shape (Postgres reconnect after insert connection errors plus worker health state and stall warning), but will not force-add private ops files to a public PR. Releasing this item for a private deployment-path change."
